Class Item

java.lang.Object
  data.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ContinuousItem, DiscreteItem
public abstract class Item
extends Object
implements Serializable

La classe astratta Item modella un generico item (coppia attributo-valore, per esempio Outlook=”Sunny”).
